- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses coordination in dynamic distributed systems. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is relevant as the paper uses modal formulas to represent how values should be combined. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems) is also relevant as the paper discusses autonomous behaviors of components in distributed systems.
